sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM_Inf as vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/S
    participant vLLM_Emb as vLLM Embedding<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/S
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Search as Search API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VecDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant FilProc as File Processor<br/>(inline/Docling)

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Client Inference Request
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Forward inference request<br/>Auth: API Token (Bearer)<br/>TLS configurable
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: LLM completion response
    OGX->>PG: Log inference request<br/>Auth: Username/Password<br/>Plaintext
    OGX-->>Client: JSON response (streaming or batch)

    Note over Client,Search: Flow 2: Agentic Response with Tool Use
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/responses<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Initial inference (tool selection)<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: Response with tool_calls
    OGX->>Search: Execute web search<br/>(Tavily/Brave)<br/>Auth: API Key<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Search-->>OGX: Search results
    OGX->>PG: Persist agent state<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Follow-up inference (with context)<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: Final response
    OGX-->>Client: Agentic response with tool outputs

    Note over Client,VecDB: Flow 3: RAG with Vector Store
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/files (upload document)<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>FilProc: Process document<br/>(Docling/PyPDF/MarkItDown)
    FilProc-->>OGX: Extracted text chunks
    OGX->>vLLM_Emb: Generate embeddings<br/>Auth: API Token<br/>TLS configurable
    vLLM_Emb-->>OGX: Embedding vectors
    OGX->>VecDB: Store vectors<br/>Auth: Token/Password<br/>TLS configurable
    VecDB-->>OGX: Stored confirmation
    Client->>OGX: POST /v1/responses (RAG query)<br/>Auth: OAuth2 Bearer (optional)
    OGX->>VecDB: Similarity search<br/>Auth: Token/Password
    VecDB-->>OGX: Relevant chunks
    OGX->>vLLM_Inf: Inference with retrieved context<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM_Inf-->>OGX: Contextual response
    OGX-->>Client: RAG-augmented response
